| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0307 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 62c8ff6f-e712-5f0f-b29d-871d938b53b2"
